tracking.coverageType: DJ Horne gathers the rock and drains the 3-pointer from deep as the Sun Devils take a 9-0 lead.

videos.headline: DJ Horne steps up and knocks down a deep 3 for Arizona State

videos.description: Jay Heath hauls in the dime from Jalen Graham and knocks down a 3-pointer for the Sun Devils.
videos.headline: Jay Heath drains the long 3 to put Arizona State on the board first

videos.description: Kimani Lawrence gets the crowd on their feet as he throws it down with authority for the Sun Devils.
videos.headline: Kimani Lawrence raises the roof with this thunderous jam

videos.description: Jalen Graham gathers the rock and throws down the massive jam to extend the Sun Devils' lead. (edited)
videos.headline: Kimani Lawrence somehow gets the rock to Jalen Graham for the jam

videos.description: Bennedict Mathurin steps up and knocks down a 3-pointer to pull the Wildcats within two.
videos.headline: Bennedict Mathurin drains it from beyond the arc for Arizona

videos.description: Bennedict Mathurin soars through the paint and lays in the nearly full-court dime from Kerr Kriisa to extend the Wildcats' lead.
videos.headline: Kerr Kriisa's long pass sets up Bennedict Mathurin for an Arizona bucket

videos.description: Dalen Terry gathers the rock and soars through the paint for the massive jam.
videos.headline: Dalen Terry throws down the hammer for Arizona

videos.description: Dalen Terry gets the steal and finishes with the acrobatic layup to extend the Wildcats' lead in the second half.
videos.headline: Dalen Terry gets it done on both sides of the ball for Arizona
